Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.42,0:01:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 因為是試做
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,先做200g試試看吧 白玉糰子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.67,0:01:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.02,0:01:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,名字就叫涼白玉糖漿 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.13,0:01:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 絕對很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.54,0:01:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,每年慣例的夏天的商店街祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.87,0:01:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,三日月堂也要出攤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.74,0:02:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,今年 爺爺把點心設計交給了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.37,0:02:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,白玉糰子的做法 簡單說來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,一 把白玉粉加水攪拌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.56,0:02:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,二 團起來煮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.84,0:02:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧 很簡單吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.48,0:02:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,簡單… 真的太簡單了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.09,0:02:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,白玉粉200g 大約配160cc水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.36,0:02:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,在碗裡放粉 然後一點點加水攪拌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,拌勻後使勁揉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.31,0:02:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,加水太多會發黏難以團成團
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,加水到白玉粉成團就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.46,0:02:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,用手揉成棒狀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,掐成一口大小
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.49,0:02:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我開始掌握要領了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:02:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,做這個好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:03:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,糰子 這個是小桃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,小桃做得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不過有點大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 這麼大行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,太小了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,小~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,圓的就行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係 煮過會膨脹一點 大小正好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,如果白玉糰子比較大 就這樣捏出個豁口來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但這次是小粒的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,然後把它放進沸水裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,過上兩三分鐘就會咕嘟咕嘟浮起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.92,0:03:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.17,0:03:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,再煮一會兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,然後再煮1分鐘左右
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.54,0:03:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,放進冰水裡 涼一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.19,0:03:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs54}Q彈~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好快 好簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.06,0:03:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 先簡單的用砂糖醬油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,QQ的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.86,0:04:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,白玉糰子自身這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.39,0:04:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,問題在於糖漿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.68,0:04:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,有抹茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,梅子糖漿 涼紅豆湯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,果然抹茶的好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,可是抹茶太貴了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不想賣一杯300日元以上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,白玉粉200g
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,大概可以做小個兒白玉丸子60個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.26,0:04:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 那涼奶茶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.53,0:04:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,微微帶點甜味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.07,0:04:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,確實紅茶的茶葉要便宜得多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那不如連黑珍珠都放進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.18,0:04:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,也能點綴一下顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這個好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,既然黑珍珠要花錢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.66,0:05:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,容器和勺子不用一次性的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,而是把咱家和三日月堂的 還有美咲阿姨店裡的聚集起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,洗過循環利用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然有點累
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 讓桐山君來洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好辦法 就拜託他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,糰子做得還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.76,0:05:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有用冰水泡過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.09,0:05:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,然後是黑珍珠嗎 真時髦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.48,0:05:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,口感真好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這是澱粉的一種吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,外公
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.73,0:05:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,…這個怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.14,0:05:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺年輕人會喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,很適合在小攤上大賣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟是祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.46,0:06:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,特別是這個好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.61,0:06:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,梅子糖漿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.09,0:06:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽口 好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這是千惠做的梅子糖漿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 有股梅子香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.88,0:06:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,放暑假之後不久
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我就去見千惠了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.72,0:06:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,千惠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,她帶我參觀了牧場
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:06:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,陪我玩 汪汪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.26,0:06:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,陪我玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,給我看了小花的小狗們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡 喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.19,0:07:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,交談途中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,千惠有時會默默的發呆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.95,0:07:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,根據佐藤老師的說法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.26,0:07:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,千惠現在看到初中女生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.71,0:07:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,也會僵住動彈不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,看到同齡的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.86,0:07:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,痛苦的事 難受的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,都會一股腦的湧向胸口和心頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,身體在拚命地抵抗這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:08:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,為了一點點恢復像從前那樣的說話行動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.56,0:08:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,千惠在這裡一步一步的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,老師這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.46,0:08:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,傍晚 千惠發燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,她的媽媽開車把我們送去了車站
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真的謝謝你和千惠做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,她媽媽好多次握住了我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,她說會在這裡和千惠一起加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,首先是交動物朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,然後是年長的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,第三個步驟是交同齡的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.97,0:09:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,千惠現在也在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,給千惠發夏日祭的照片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,大家在享用梅子糖漿的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,然後 還要再去見她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是三日月堂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,冰冰的 甜甜的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,冰鎮白玉糖漿怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.66,0:09:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,冰冰甜甜的白玉糖漿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.49,0:09:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,冰鎮的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.37,0:09:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,梅子糖漿久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.92,0:09:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,新碗來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊的收了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.47,0:10:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝 桐山君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.22,0:10:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,還有百日元硬幣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,拆兩條放裡面了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,還有抹布 新的掛這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,桐山君太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.77,0:10:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼這麼了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 小子 讓你幫這麼大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,來喝冰鎮糖漿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,客人好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,盛況空前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,連我這邊都賣得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次參加這種活動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺好吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,桐山君 桐山君 來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 高橋君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.03,0:10:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 你是不是又變大了很多？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.52,0:11:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,這是千惠做的梅子糖漿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.57,0:11:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好大個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,奶奶 美香子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.03,0:11:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃的三色糰子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,要來一串嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.39,0:11:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.97,0:11:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,她們做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,真是個好晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,小零
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡這種的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:12:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,最喜歡這種了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.51,0:12:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.43,0:12:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,還不到7點 一轉眼就賣了這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,現在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,廚房裡留著當晚飯的咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,也能賣到飛起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.75,0:12:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,咖哩不行 我們家是和果子店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.86,0:12:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不好了 姐姐 白玉已經只剩一盒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.18,0:12:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,明明做了這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.95,0:12:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,來煮吧 現在馬上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.99,0:12:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了 因為糖漿已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.02,0:12:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣 難得是個大賺一筆的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不是還有黃豆粉和黑蜜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,外公
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,明里 燒水去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.38,0:12:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,日向這邊拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,小子去買冰來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.37,0:13:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,問高橋家兒子就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.43,0:13:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我來做糰子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好 川本家 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:11.98,SCREEN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\c&H7A6F72&\fs65\blur1\b1\pos(1785,1060)}在 這 裡
Comment: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,==============================================B-Title==================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:15.98,SCREEN,,0,0,0,,{\an1\c&HC0F35D&\fs65\blur1\b1\pos(132,450)}暑 假{\fs42}  ①
Comment: 0,0:22:54.69,0:22:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,==============================================B-PART=================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.35,0:13:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,三月町祭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,多準備點糖漿就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到7點就賣光了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好浪費
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,話說你們成本太高了  送太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.95,0:13:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,費那麼大勁才賺這麼點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.04,0:13:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,可真是賠本賺吆喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,客人來了這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,果然會讓人熱血沸騰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.34,0:13:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,多虧來了好多客人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,平時的點心也賣出好多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,吸引顧客的拳頭商品果然重要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,超市說牛奶一盒128日元也會去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.84,0:14:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,雞胸肉100g68日元
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,西紅柿罐一個78日元什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.61,0:14:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,其他的東西當然也會一併買了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你們的媽媽和外婆也很會賣東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,甜的 鹹的 不管做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,總能讓顧客排長隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,每次祭典 我都覺得真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,真想讓你們也看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.47,0:14:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我還記得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,喵喵燒 花花燒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.22,0:14:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,大大的蝴蝶結的袋子 好可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:14:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,她們常說不要花錢 要用心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我也幫忙包裝了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.01,0:15:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你們作為第一次已經做得很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然銷售額 手法和預判都還差點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,明年也可以繼續交給你們哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？ 可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.82,0:15:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我會加油的 像媽媽和外婆那樣讓顧客排起長隊來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,得快點去考慮菜單才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,日向 冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,或者說先要考試
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.67,0:15:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,要報哪個學校？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.25,0:15:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,明天是暑期考試
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.19,0:15:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然是暑假 但也要去上學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.34,0:15:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,出題範圍已經學過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 學了 雖然還剩了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.83,0:15:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 姐姐 果凍怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,手停下了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.56,0:15:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,快點包
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,銅鑼燒都要乾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.75,0:15:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:15:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,外公 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 我… 做不來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,3A的班主任 不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.06,0:16:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事沒事 多半…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.59,0:16:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,姑且還有我在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,擔子太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到了吧 那個高城家長的態度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.27,0:16:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我絕對沒自信和她周旋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,換班主任了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,要把重要的初三後期交給這麼年輕的傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,學校在想什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 我還是新人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是新人我就是老人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不如說要我負責兩個班 體力上完全不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,一個人怎麼可能看得過來90人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我還有年級主任的工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.78,0:17:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 和高城的談話 要持續到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我說過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,讓她知道自己做了什麼 也是工作的一環
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然你這樣說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不論對她再說什麼都沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.78,0:17:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,因為她自己決定不要去理解罪惡感這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要對她費這麼大力氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.14,0:17:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,多奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,給人添麻煩的一方反而受到這麼多照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,被欺負的佐倉千惠不僅轉學了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,在對面也還沒能上學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.07,0:17:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,讓一百步 就算她真的沒有惡意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.47,0:17:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不如說 都做到這個地步了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.18,0:17:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不論有沒有惡意都是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.06,0:17:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,小見川…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:17:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我要寫在檔案裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,作為新班主任
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,把真正情況一五一十寫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,獨善其身 對其他人攻擊性強
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.14,0:18:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,作為集團首領
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.37,0:18:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,在班級內部引起了大規模問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.46,0:18:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,對於自己造成的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.64,0:18:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,誰都必須負起責任
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,必須受到報應
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不然很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我說 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有答案了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.58,0:18:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人都必須努力的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你找了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.26,0:19:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 那之後我想了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.43,0:19:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,沒能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,沒能找到是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.02,0:19:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我絞盡了腦汁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.42,0:19:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但仔細想想 一個都沒能想出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不可思議啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼說來 仔細想想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我對於這一點從來沒有懷疑過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.67,0:19:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然努力很累
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但我只知道必須去做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不知不覺間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:20:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,都會到達“努力是為了自己”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.48,0:20:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,已經不記得是誰說的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,還是從哪裡讀到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼司空見慣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,到了這一把年紀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,終於發自內心的想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 這句話是真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.07,0:20:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我長久以來肯定只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,想要做個比現在更好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,突然說起自己的事了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.73,0:20:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,會很長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.71,0:20:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.79,0:20:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.04,0:20:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你們班的臨時班主任就做到今天為止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,高城
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你現在多半不安到無可奈何吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼都沒有做過 連自己的極限都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不安的原因就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你之所以提不起幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.03,0:21:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是因為害怕知道自己的極限而失望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,可是高城
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,失望也不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,只有知道自己的極限在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.31,0:21:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,才能知道應當去做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.80,0:21:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,只要搞清楚自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.69,0:21:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,就能漸漸看到自己想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.30,0:21:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣一來 就能從現在這份極度不安中解放出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.88,0:21:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,只有這一點 我可以保證
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.17,0:21:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,考試結束後的晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:22:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我畫了好多畫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.97,0:22:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,腦子裡冒出好多顏色漂亮的點心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.28,0:22:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不斷冒出來 冒出來 停不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.90,0:22:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,日向 還要熬夜到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.02,0:22:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,快點去泡澡…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.93,0:22:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,還開著風扇 會感冒的 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.58,0:22:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,日向…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.04,0:22:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼晚了搞什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.13,0:22:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.39,0:22:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.38,0:22:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,全都看起來好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.47,0:22:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.39,0:22:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.27,0:23:00.02,SCREEN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\c&H7A6F72&\fs65\blur1\b1\pos(1795,1060)}暑 假{\fs42}  ①
Comment: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,==============================================C-PART================================================
